[
  {
    "startTime": 1.134,
    "endTime": 2.368,
    "text": "I want to share some of my favorite"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.368,
    "endTime": 3.402,
    "text": "\"Why I'm Single\" stories from you guys. Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.402,
    "endTime": 5.538,
    "text": "This first one is from @wickedclos."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.538,
    "endTime": 6.673,
    "text": "He says, \"I order my food at the drive-thru with my regular voice,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.7,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "then pretend I have a passenger and use another voice so they don't think it's all for one person."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.514,
    "endTime": 17.45,
    "text": "Can I get a Big Mac?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.45,
    "endTime": 19.819,
    "text": "[ Southern accent ] Yeah, and two cheeseburgers!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 19.819,
    "endTime": 21.421,
    "text": "And two cheeseburgers."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 21.421,
    "endTime": 23.489,
    "text": "[ Southern accent ] Super-size that thing, man!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.489,
    "endTime": 24.624000000000002,
    "text": "Can you super-size --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.624,
    "endTime": 25.758,
    "text": "Hey, let me order, all right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.758,
    "endTime": 27.86,
    "text": "What happens when they pull up, though?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.86,
    "endTime": 29.561,
    "text": "Where's the other dude?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.562,
    "endTime": 32.131,
    "text": "This one's from @KatyDombroski."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.131,
    "endTime": 33.266,
    "text": "She says, \"I tried flirting with a guy by saying his smile was nice."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.3,
    "endTime": 38.0,
    "text": "He said he got it from his mom. I replied,\" Your mom must be hot then.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 42.675000000000004,
    "text": "-Blblblblbl! -What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 44.644,
    "endTime": 47.147,
    "text": "This one from Avi Abrahamsen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.147,
    "endTime": 48.348,
    "text": "He says, \"The last time I was leaving a restaurant, the hostess said, \"Enjoy your night,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.4,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "and I said, \"Love you too!\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.756,
    "endTime": 60.159,
    "text": "This one's from @NicoleAsselin1."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.159,
    "endTime": 61.628,
    "text": "She says, \"Whenever I wear ripped jeans, I only shave the patches of leg hair that will be exposed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.502,
    "endTime": 71.17,
    "text": "That's good spatial awareness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.238,
    "endTime": 73.573,
    "text": "Those are very hairy knees."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.14,
    "endTime": 78.77,
    "text": "This one's from @KSchafheimer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.77,
    "endTime": 79.679,
    "text": "She says, \"Last night, I punched myself in the face with both hands trying to take my quilt out of the dryer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.851,
    "endTime": 87.42,
    "text": "That's cute. That's cute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.42,
    "endTime": 90.59,
    "text": "I don't think -- You shouldn't be single for that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.159,
    "endTime": 97.29700000000001,
    "text": "This one's from @demaskingtape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 99.165,
    "endTime": 100.60000000000001,
    "text": "De-masking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.6,
    "endTime": 102.35,
    "text": "De-masking, Am I missing something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.35,
    "endTime": 104.503,
    "text": "-No. Masking tape. De-masking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.503,
    "endTime": 106.706,
    "text": "I know masking tape. De-masking?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.706,
    "endTime": 107.974,
    "text": "Is that, like, to de-mask?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.974,
    "endTime": 109.308,
    "text": "-De-mask somebody? -\"Phantom of the Opera\" thing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.1,
    "endTime": 112.67899999999999,
    "text": "Hey, how did he get that mask, the phantom of the opera?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.679,
    "endTime": 113.913,
    "text": "He made it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.913,
    "endTime": 115.648,
    "text": "-So he like -- Did he smelt it or something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.648,
    "endTime": 117.18299999999999,
    "text": "Got his face burned with acid or whatever,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.183,
    "endTime": 118.48400000000001,
    "text": "and then he made that mask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.484,
    "endTime": 119.818,
    "text": "Does he start with a balloon?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.819,
    "endTime": 121.19,
    "text": "I think he starts with a balloon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.21,
    "endTime": 123.389,
    "text": "And then you use already-read --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.389,
    "endTime": 124.957,
    "text": "yesterday's newspaper. -Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.957,
    "endTime": 126.759,
    "text": "Some flour, water."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.759,
    "endTime": 129.762,
    "text": "-Or,  he uses plaster of Paris."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 129.762,
    "endTime": 131.33,
    "text": "'Cause that's where he is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 131.33,
    "endTime": 132.965,
    "text": "He does that on there. -That's true, yeah. Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.965,
    "endTime": 134.466,
    "text": "So, there, they call it..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.466,
    "endTime": 135.30100000000002,
    "text": "Plaster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.301,
    "endTime": 136.702,
    "text": "-That's correct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.702,
    "endTime": 139.38,
    "text": "And so the phantom makes the thing, and he cuts it out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.38,
    "endTime": 140.39,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.39,
    "endTime": 141.6,
    "text": "Finds the eye hole."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 141.7,
    "endTime": 142.441,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.441,
    "endTime": 143.943,
    "text": "-You know. -Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.77,
    "endTime": 146.679,
    "text": "So he can see."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.679,
    "endTime": 149.51500000000001,
    "text": "The music and the movement of the plaster of Paris mask"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.515,
    "endTime": 152.82999999999998,
    "text": "But why --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.84,
    "endTime": 154.854,
    "text": "Is this part of his face that good?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.854,
    "endTime": 156.222,
    "text": "Well..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.222,
    "endTime": 158.591,
    "text": "Like, why not just do -- you know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.692,
    "endTime": 161.36,
    "text": "Like, one of those -- a regular mask."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.428,
    "endTime": 163.829,
    "text": "I'm still the phantom of the opera."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.829,
    "endTime": 165.531,
    "text": "-Right. -I look cooler than --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.531,
    "endTime": 167.567,
    "text": "Who wears a one-sided mask?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.567,
    "endTime": 169.668,
    "text": "A dude with one side of his face missing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.873,
    "endTime": 175.875,
    "text": "One side of his face? I never saw the play."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.976,
    "endTime": 178.177,
    "text": "Apparently this side of the face got --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.177,
    "endTime": 179.245,
    "text": "One side of his face is missing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.245,
    "endTime": 180.28,
    "text": "Yeah, it got burnt or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.28,
    "endTime": 181.447,
    "text": "Doesn't mean it's missing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 181.447,
    "endTime": 183.249,
    "text": "There was a fire at the Paris Opera House,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.249,
    "endTime": 184.517,
    "text": "and he's ashamed of it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.517,
    "endTime": 185.751,
    "text": "There was a fire at his parents' house,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.751,
    "endTime": 186.81900000000002,
    "text": "so he moved into the subway? -No, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.819,
    "endTime": 188.22,
    "text": "The Paris Opera House..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.22,
    "endTime": 189.788,
    "text": "-Oh, the Paris Opera House. -...not his parents' house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.788,
    "endTime": 191.223,
    "text": "Oh, I thought you said a fire at his parents house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.223,
    "endTime": 192.358,
    "text": "I think I've seen it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.358,
    "endTime": 193.659,
    "text": "Anyways,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.659,
    "endTime": 196.296,
    "text": "I love \"Phantom of the Opera\" and Andrew Lloyd Webber."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.264,
    "endTime": 199.93200000000002,
    "text": "This is from"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.71,
    "endTime": 206.639,
    "text": "That's an Andrew Lloyd Webber joint, isn't it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.874,
    "endTime": 212.644,
    "text": "This one is from demaskingtape."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.644,
    "endTime": 214.746,
    "text": "Oh! Like the phantom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.25,
    "endTime": 219.51,
    "text": "-You're saying that the phantom"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 220.186,
    "endTime": 221.588,
    "text": "She says, \"I once ate a dog biscuit on accident, and then again on purpose because it tasted just like a Mini Muffin."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.36,
    "endTime": 228.52700000000002,
    "text": "Don't eat dog biscuits."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.527,
    "endTime": 230.396,
    "text": "That is ruff."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.396,
    "endTime": 233.79799999999997,
    "text": "This one is from @MetalFanInBlack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.799,
    "endTime": 235.201,
    "text": "He says, \"I'm single because I'd probably have to update my wardrobe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.802,
    "endTime": 237.904,
    "text": "Look at this picture."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.904,
    "endTime": 240.37199999999999,
    "text": "Oh, my goodness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.372,
    "endTime": 243.275,
    "text": "I want to thank Simon Cowell for sending in that --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.144,
    "endTime": 246.278,
    "text": "Or the phantom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.278,
    "endTime": 248.79,
    "text": "Or the phantom of the opera wears the black."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.8,
    "endTime": 249.848,
    "text": "What happened at the end"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.848,
    "endTime": 250.983,
    "text": "of \"Phantom of the Opera?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.983,
    "endTime": 251.984,
    "text": "Do they get married?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 532.2,
    "endTime": 534.589,
    "text": "I think he burns alive, doesn't he?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 534.589,
    "endTime": 535.7600000000001,
    "text": "That's just a guess. That's just a guess."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.76,
    "endTime": 544.17,
    "text": "Does he really? Have you seen it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 544.17,
    "endTime": 554.03,
    "text": "-Me? -Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 554.03,
    "endTime": 560.769,
    "text": "Nah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 560.769,
    "endTime": 569.03,
    "text": "-No one in this -- No one's seen \"Phantom of the Opera?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 569.03,
    "endTime": 571.579,
    "text": "Wait, Stro says he saw it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 571.579,
    "endTime": 579.1999999999999,
    "text": "-What happened? -What happens at the end?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 579.2,
    "endTime": 582.2900000000001,
    "text": "I don't remember."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.29,
    "endTime": 587.05,
    "text": "Why would you even say that you saw?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.05,
    "endTime": 591.12,
    "text": "This last one -- -Oh, thank God."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 591.12,
    "endTime": 599.839,
    "text": "The last one is -- \"I saw it, I saw it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 599.839,
    "endTime": 606.36,
    "text": "I don't remember anything."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.36,
    "endTime": 609.86,
    "text": "This last one's from U.S. ski team member, Lindsey Vonn,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 609.86,
    "endTime": 618.8100000000001,
    "text": "our pal!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 618.81,
    "endTime": 624.27,
    "text": "What?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 624.27,
    "endTime": 630.18,
    "text": "She played the hashtag game, \"Why I'm Single.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 630.18,
    "endTime": 634.9899999999999,
    "text": "She said, \"I'm single because I only have"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.99,
    "endTime": 647.1,
    "text": "eyes for the Olympics.\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 647.1,
    "endTime": 646.1800000000001,
    "text": "\"Also, where's my pep talk, coach?\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.18,
    "endTime": 652.3389999999999,
    "text": "Oh, I did promise her."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.339,
    "endTime": 660.149,
    "text": "I promised Lindsey I would do a pep talk before the Olympics."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 660.149,
    "endTime": 664.589,
    "text": "So, they start tomorrow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 664.589,
    "endTime": 673.11,
    "text": "Do you guys mind if I give Team USA a little pep talk?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.11,
    "endTime": 675.0600000000001,
    "text": "All right. Give me. Give me my onesie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "Here we go. All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.06,
    "endTime": 680.6999999999999,
    "text": "I've got to put my onesie on here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 680.7,
    "endTime": 685.73,
    "text": "Quest, can I get a drumroll?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.73,
    "endTime": 693.72,
    "text": "Got to get my rat tail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.72,
    "endTime": 696.4200000000001,
    "text": "Hey, team USA."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.42,
    "endTime": 703.2099999999999,
    "text": "Do it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 703.21,
    "endTime": 707.48,
    "text": "Just do it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.48,
    "endTime": 712.64,
    "text": "You're going to the Olympics! I need you to ski!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 712.64,
    "endTime": 717.6999999999999,
    "text": "Bronze did it, silver did it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 717.7,
    "endTime": 724.4200000000001,
    "text": "So do it! Be the gold!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 724.42,
    "endTime": 730.389,
    "text": "Ski down the hill! Speed skate!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 730.389,
    "endTime": 734.1800000000001,
    "text": "Triple Lutz!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 734.18,
    "endTime": 739.9399999999999,
    "text": "Sweep the ice! Curl!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 739.94,
    "endTime": 747.3800000000001,
    "text": "You're the best, so be the best, and beat the best!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 747.38,
    "endTime": 752.02,
    "text": "Do it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 752.02,
    "endTime": 756.9499999999999,
    "text": "Good luck to all the athletes"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 756.95,
    "endTime": 760.9100000000001,
    "text": "competing in the Winter Games next week."
  }
]